Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is hard to define.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the reason is suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What docs the cross mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a coded case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where did I see him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man with the black hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, why do I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like something will break...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right it's just like that time, that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An unsettling feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you paying attention to the lesson. Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what is that mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cross? No, an X?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will have to tell us at the beginning of the next class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a very important symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially for ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's such a cute mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O.K.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Secret Rushed Omission. Part 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,X?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's supposed to have a special meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} mentioned it at the end of class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a cute mark, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, now now, it isn't something a kid would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} often knows unusual things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,X... X... X...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,X is a variable in algebra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or it can also mean a question, the unknown, or the unexplained...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,X could mean as in X-rated, only 18 and above...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The X-Ray would be Roentgen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's actually a cross...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cross would mean error or reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"X1" would mean once divorced...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right, she said it was an important mark for women.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, my mom often writes them at the end of her letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she has never told me what they mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Sonoko, don't you think that Jodie-sense's teaching has changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right, she was so serious before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now it's fun because of the English expressions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi, even with those compliments I won't make the exam easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, have you figured out X?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, why don't you send a message and ask Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say "I'll give you my special X if you tell me the answer."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"l give you my X!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the... What is X?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,X... X... X...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:06:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was something I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we hang out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,X... X...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A groper?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there one we should know of?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teitan schoolgirls have become victims on buses and subways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hasn't happened to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if one of them tried to get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran would use her karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could follow you all the way home, waiting for their only chance to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cute, cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a stalker could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a stalker came to my house, my security would chase him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't noticed anyone around my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you sec anyone like that, tell me immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:19.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Japanese people still don't know how dangerous stalkers can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you tell me. I'll teach that stalker a lesson the American way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? A suspicious man is following you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm in front of the building you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said a suspicious man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's likely just the guy I've been investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:55.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He's probably wanting to negotiate a better deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may offer me twice as much as you, if I forget the things I found on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The money will determine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pay three, no four times as much, just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring me the evidence and his name now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be there in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how it's gonna be, unless you can match his offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, following me won't make things any easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of your criminal activities are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this a blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, but you've experienced a blackout in a building before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Suzuki-sad call the police and an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that written on the envelope?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Circle, cross, triangle"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stabbed in the stomach with a blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the victim was Chuujou Katsunori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age forty-three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to his card, he owns a detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what I don't get is this "dying message"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dying message!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:40.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Jodie Saintemillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nice to see you again. Keiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She should improve her Japanese before correcting anyone's English.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to get involved in cases often.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:11:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but not as many as those girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were talking in that cafe until the blackout happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the lights came back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came out here and found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, the blackout occurred because of an error made by an electrician during maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It lasted for less than fifteen seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the criminal took advantage of this coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wrote this strange dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Message Just after he was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what's the meaning of these symbols?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they can replace characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible that this could be someone's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I've seen these marks before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please think. Jodie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Controller! On a Japanese game's controller!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where I've seen those marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Docs that help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Sensei's a gamer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Meguro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The call history says a call came thirty minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thirty minutes ago? That's the time of the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's return the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it was you that called Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} thirty minutes ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it have been that phone call!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy was talking weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see. I think it was: "I'll pay four times as much, just hurry."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hired a detective to investigate your company?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We discovered that someone was embezzling money from the company last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An executive ordered me to find out who it was before the president found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is your company?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're located in this building on floors eight to eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, after the detective discovered the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You arranged to meet him at that cafe to avoid a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, he didn't show at the arranged time, so you decided to call him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The envelope Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was holding turned up empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that the embezzler and the killer are the same person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he may have killed the detective and retreated to an office upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, do you have any idea who the embezzler is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, just last week the detective mailed me a partial report with a list of all the suspicious employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here is the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, checking all of them won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A list of fifty-eight suspects...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the only clue is "circle, cross, triangle."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lab has determined that the "circle, cross, triangle" symbols have the victim's fingerprints on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we thought, it seems Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} drew them himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So after being attacked by the culprit, Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} must have drawn the symbols as a dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Message...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To help identify the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, it seems Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was stabbed before the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to a witness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lights went out just as Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was stabbed by a man in a coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stabbing happened at the foot of this escalator
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was most likely stabbed in a struggle over the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the lights came back on. Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was crouching near the escalator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man in the coat then approached the victim, stole the documents inside the envelope, and ran up the escalator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then. Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} must have started drawing the symbols while he was here, at the foot of the escalator?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Likely during the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that even though he was able to keep the envelope, the criminal was still able to get the documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how he died and ended up at the top of the escalator, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why didn't that witness scream after seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She thought they were filming a suspense drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, we can assume that the embezzler is the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All we have to do now is figure out what "circle, cross, triangle" means, and from this list of fifty-eight employees...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find out which one it refers to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the "cross" from "circle, cross, triangle" may refer to the X from mathematics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why "circle, cross, triangle?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "circle" and "triangle" could have been to throw off the criminal from suspecting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! So the criminal's good at math.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is anyone in your company good at math?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we primarily focus on recruiting those who are adept at different languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were "triangle, circle, square" it would be Oden...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe the "cross" refers to that X.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the cute mark Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, it can't be that X.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean the X girls put at the end of letters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Takagi, do you know what that X means?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, you must get those types of letters often.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, just an occasional tease...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that "X mean anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it has nothing to do with the "circle, cross, triangle" from this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe there's more to this than "circle, cross, triangle."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There 's something to the left of the "circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that mean there was something else besides "circle, cross, triangle" written here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, we noticed that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't find anything to the left of the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, have you checked...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The steps of the escalator?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the moment the escalator isn't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it possible the blood is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the escalator was moving for a while, wouldn't it have wiped away the blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's alright
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there's a chemical that can make the blood reappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Officer Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luminol should highlight the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the victim wrote that while crouching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be easy to tell which step it was, because it should still be covered in blood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there is one tiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is X?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one that Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a bit too young to know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanski{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I need you to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure. I believe this coat, this hat, and these gloves belonged to the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found them in the restroom on the 5th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately, there was no sign of the documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what about the checking of the suspects' alibis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, were checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many of the employees were either eating or sleeping alone during the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:21:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the list, we could only confirm alibis from twenty-seven of the fifty-eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That leaves thirty-one without alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were still searching for the "document, primarily focusing on floors eight through eleven".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good, everyone continue searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now there are thirty-one suspects...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only clue we have are those symbols.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if they don't find anything on the escalator...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we found another symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, it's actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A "square"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be the kanji for month, or the katakana for "ro".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you consider the other symbols, it's probably a square.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This doesn't help any...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it matches the shape on the envelope. Chuujou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} must have made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That "square..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is larger than the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What docs that mean?
